&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;3D-printed cornea&lt;/strong&gt; was created from &lt;strong&gt;human donor corneal tissue&lt;/strong&gt; by a team of researchers from the&lt;strong&gt; L V Prasad Eye Institute (LVPEI), Hyderabad, Indian Institute of Technology Hyderabad (IITH)&lt;/strong&gt;, and the &lt;strong&gt;Center for Cellular and Molecular Biology (CCMB), Hyderabad.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The cornea created via 3D printing is&lt;strong&gt; natural, free of artificial materials, &lt;/strong&gt;and&lt;strong&gt; safe for patients to use.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;By &lt;strong&gt;sealing the corneal perforation &lt;/strong&gt;and&lt;strong&gt; preventing infection&lt;/strong&gt; during war-related injuries or in a distant place without a &lt;strong&gt;tertiary eye care centre&lt;/strong&gt;, the &lt;strong&gt;bio-ink used&lt;/strong&gt; to create this 3D-printed cornea could save the sight of&lt;strong&gt; army men.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The cornea is the &lt;strong&gt;clear outer layer &lt;/strong&gt;at the &lt;strong&gt;front of the eye.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The cornea aids in your&lt;strong&gt; eye&amp;#39;s ability to focus light &lt;/strong&gt;for &lt;strong&gt;clear vision.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Important roles&lt;/strong&gt; played by the &lt;strong&gt;cornea in the eye:&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
